[{"chunk":{"content":"**Title:** **Developing AI tailored immunocytokines to target melanoma\nbrain metastases**\n\n**Background:** Brain metastases (BMs) occur in almost 50% of patients\nwith metastatic melanoma, resulting in a dismal prognosis with a poor\noverall survival for most patients. Metastases arise from primary tumor\nclones capable of adapting to new environments and are frequently\nresistant to therapies to which the primary tumor was sensitive.\nParticularly in BMs, the milieu of the brain creates a highly\nimmunosuppressive tumor microenvironment (TME). Single-cell technologies\ntogether with machine learning have emerged as powerful tools to\ndecipher complex interactions between cells in the TME, enabling\ndevelopment of data driven designs of immunotherapies. In this project,\nwe aim to harness these tools to gain in depth understanding of melanoma\nBM TMEs immunosuppression, and to develop novel cytokine-based\napproaches that turn the BM TME from immunologically \"cold\" to \"hot\".","content_hash":"ecf71342975a0eb40fe12000d248998228e79a4e08fa743ae2cd11c4d765c103","index":0,"element_type":"raw"},"embedding":[-0.04256473854184151,0.0220511332154274,0.03610008582472801,-0.031065979972481728,-0.018961716443300247,0.002576742321252823,-0.08922318369150162,0.019824190065264702,0.0684828981757164,0.00022502821229863912,-0.05391395464539528,-0.0643337070941925,0.030608870089054108,-0.07979900389909744,0.04700545221567154,0.03240238130092621,0.08303355425596237,-0.07185838371515274,-0.019734416157007217,-0.004218614660203457,0.010093221440911293,-0.04501267522573471,-0.059480831027030945,-0.0471557192504406,0.006750110536813736,0.00428858632221818,-0.029567690566182137,-0.06511356681585312,0.0015800807159394026,-0.0040978635661304,0.03572046756744385,0.03554021194577217,0.03080824948847294,-0.07637349516153336,0.005589248146861792,-0.003778844838961959,0.03882945328950882,0.00804292131215334,0.010674714110791683,0.00906516145914793,0.0415559783577919,-0