53868039697409,0.016304505988955498,-0.06230095401406288,-0.09092982858419418,-0.04062587022781372,-0.005797788500785828,-0.020168738439679146,-0.02098640613257885,-0.019581014290452003,0.0813613086938858,-0.10137003660202026,-0.08553050458431244,-0.06679613143205643,-0.047322534024715424,-0.026579828932881355,0.03382246568799019,-0.00035845040110871196,0.0444093756377697,-0.014701665379106998,0.02606728859245777,0.011187494732439518,-0.09388680756092072,0.024692477658391,0.026193231344223022,0.015245199203491211,0.05933923274278641,0.005332398694008589,-0.0032024008687585592,0.055024921894073486,-0.028638098388910294,0.05727839469909668,-0.058260682970285416,-0.04668063670396805,0.04380398988723755,0.05757473036646843,-0.02139807678759098,-0.0511147566139698,-0.07858987897634506,0.011452971026301384,-0.005967068485915661,0.03486904129385948,0.007955051958560944,-0.060488440096378326,-0.026659267023205757,-0.042820438742637634,-0.03259584307670593,0.005124365445226431,-0.06054503843188286,-0.011349101550877094,-0.03788657858967781,0.02357790619134903,0.016821783035993576,-0.018213383853435516,0.12930653989315033,-0.016519498080015182],"file_id":"422e5c03-d3a1-4f02-8666-0cf70930a235"},{"chunk":{"content":"**Aim 2: Preclinical screening of cytokines in orthotopic\nimmunocompetent BM models.** The cytokines identified in Aim 1 will be\ntested *in vitro* and *in vivo*. First, cytokine-secreting clones of\nbrain tropic melanoma cell lines will be created by the Amit group by\ntransducing them to conditionally (dox-induced) express a broad spectrum\nof promising BM immune re-activation candidate cytokines. These clones\nwill be used to create tumor spheroids containing one or multiple\ncytokine cassettes and will be co-cultured with immune cells. By adding\ndoxycycline, we will test varied cytokine combinations. The most\neffective cytokines and cytokine combinations identified *in vitro* will\nbe used by the Weiss group for *in vivo* testing. The B16 clones\nexpressing the shortlisted cytokines or combinations will be used to\ngenerate melanoma BMs by intracardial injections. Cytokine expression\nwill be activated with doxycycline and the tumor response will be\nmonitored using MRI and survival measurement.\n\n**Aim 3: Design of tumor-targeting immunocytokines.** Potent cytokines\nthat reactivate the immune compartment and eradicated melanoma BMs will\nbe incorporated into antibody-cytokine fusion proteins (immunocytokines)\ntargeting species-conserved tumor antigens highly expressed in melanoma\nBMs. Employing melanoma BMs murine models and our advanced technologies\nfrom previous objectives, we aim at breaking through the classical\ndichotomy of response/no-response and into cycles of model-driven\noptimization. This will ultimately pinpoint the most effective\nconstructs for the IND stage.","content_hash":"412ac46e0a20c0f23d5bd8ee778a0cf34f280b3312977f08205b15c0db451891","index":2,"element_type":"raw"},"embedding":[-0.043443165719509125,0.00512949051335454,0.022838903591036797,-0.03906966745853424,-0.02314329706132412,0.010722994804382324,-0.08204058557748795,0.02547607384622097,0.053762417286634445,0.01481684111058712,-0.0494532473385334,-0.0630178153514862,0.016458433121442795,-0.09823987632989883,0.00817851535975933,0.01394775789231062,0.07837320119142532,-0.05275395140051842,-0.01033417321741581,0.0007752407109364867,-0.028681213036179543,-0.03183787688612938,-0.026195252314209938,-0.015527322888374329,0.009307103231549263,0.0008668426889926195,-0.022592991590499878,-0.04374042525887489,-0.04236866533756256,0.01563359797000885,0.018582617864012718,0.04127080738544464,0.018680041655898094,-0.048505283892154694,-0.007005130872130394,0.005183408968150616,0.013006558641791344,0.004546031821519136,-0.0004227270546834916,-0.008297954685986042,0.059050917625427246,-0.008899412117898464,0.0027384881395846605,0.01590382307767868,-0.0439845509827137,0.012973683886229992,-0.05016838014125824,0.036120589822530746,0.02590680681169033,0.0